  "title": "TRAINING INCLUDED + WEEKLY PAYOUT 💥💸",
  "description": "<h3>⚡ <strong>Sales Executive – Learn Fast, Earn Weekly</strong></h3><p>Looking for a job that doesn’t ghost you after applying?<br />We hire fast, train you properly, and <strong>pay you every week</strong>. Simple.</p><p>🛍️ What You’ll Be Doing</p><ul><li><p>Engage customers and introduce products/services</p></li><li><p>Learn how to sell (yes, <strong>training is included</strong>)</p></li><li><p>Close deals and earn commissions 💰</p></li><li><p>Work alongside a lively, supportive team</p></li><li><p>Build confidence, communication, and sales skills</p></li></ul><p>🎓 No Experience? We Got You.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Full training from Day 1</strong></p></li><li><p>Step-by-step guidance — no pressure, no guessing</p></li><li><p>Ideal for students, fresh grads, or anyone new to sales</p></li></ul><p>💸 Why This Job Slaps</p><ul><li><p><strong>WEEKLY PAYOUT</strong> (don’t wait till end of month)</p></li><li><p>Immediate start & fast recruitment</p></li><li><p>Basic pay + commission + incentives</p></li><li><p>Fun environment with real growth opportunities</p></li></ul><p>👀 Who We Want</p><ul><li><p>Friendly, motivated, and open to learning</p></li><li><p>Comfortable talking to people (or willing to try)</p></li><li><p>Ready to hustle and earn</p></li><li><p>Experience optional — attitude matters more</p></li></ul><p><strong>Work smart. Learn skills. Get paid weekly.</strong><br />Apply now — limited slots available 🚀</p>",
